name: Calligraph | The Memorial Issue, Volume 33: Issue 2
Calligraph | Studio Spaces, Volume 33: Issue 1
description:
Take a peek inside the studios of thirteen talented calligraphers and learn about their creative processes!  

We are proud to feature the studio spaces of Yukimi Annand, Nancy Campbell, Barbara Close, Marci Donley, Lisa Engelbrecht, Ellen Greenberg, Lisa Holtzman, Carrie Imai, Louis Lemoine, Phawnda Moore, Robbie Saslow, Jean Marie Seaton and Renee Troy.  

Also in this issue: Design and Interpretation for Extraordinary Letters (Liesbet Boudens), Monoline Magic (Annie Cicale), Stylized Writing (Georgia Deaver), Letters: An Expression of Culture Exhibit and the St. John's Bible Lecture at the Getty.  

Edited by Joy Deneen and designed by Alisara Tareekes.

name: Calligraph | Volume 32: Issue 1
description:
Discover new and innovative ways to organize all of your workshop notes and practice studies!  

Get inspired by the many photos and tips from Britta Brice, Lorraine Brown, Stephanie Chao, Helen Chu, Ann Lawrence, Jean Pratt, Martha Reich, Jan Saunders, DeAnn Singh and Janet Takahashi. 

Also in this issue:  SOTA+SfC@TypeCon (DeAnn Singh), Good Hues (Louise Grunewald), Ornate Pictorial Calligraph (Linda Schneider) and Experimental Water Media Collage (Jacqueline Sullivan).  

Edited by DeAnn Singh and designed by Teri Kahan.

name: SfC Tote Bag (Yellow)
description:
Perfect for workshops, travel or trips to the market, this SfC tote bag is the perfect accessory!

This tote comes in a yellow & grey color-way and the logo is printed in yellow ink.

Logo designed by the talented Lisa Engelbrecht.
